--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation requirements:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To automatically install the dependencies configure and run the install.sh script.

OCAML 4.01.0
OCAMLFIND (FINDLIB) 1.4.1

GMP 5.1.3
MPFR 3.1.2

CAMLLIB
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/bjeannet/pkg/camllib/branches/accstrat

FIXPOINT
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/bjeannet/pkg/camllib/branches/accstrat

MLGMPIDL
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/mlxxxidl/mlgmpidl/trunk

APRON
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svnroot/apron/apron/trunk

MLCUDDIDL (includes CUDD 2.4.2)
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/mlxxxidl/mlcuddidl/trunk

BDDAPRON
  svn://scm.gforge.inria.fr/svn/bjeannet/pkg/bddapron/trunk

-----------------------------
with max-strategy iteration:
-----------------------------

YICES 1.0.40 
  http://yices.csl.sri.com/download.shtml
  (GMP dynamically linked)

OCAMLYICES 
  https://github.com/polazarus/ocamlyices

EGLIB 2.6.21
  http://www.dii.uchile.cl/~daespino/EGlib_doc/main.html

QSOPT_EX 2.5.10
  http://www.dii.uchile.cl/~daespino/ESolver_doc/main.html

CAMLIDL 1.0.5
  http://caml.inria.fr/pub/old_caml_site/distrib/bazar-ocaml/camlidl-1.05.tar.gz

OCAMLQSOPT_EX
  lib/ocamlqsopt_ex

------------
with Zelus:
------------

ZELUS:
  availability to be clarified


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ReaVer is installed in the Ocamlfind package directory.

cp Makefile.config.model Makefile.config

-- set paths and features in Makefile.config

make
make install